  "description": "SIPVicious OSS is a VoIP security testing toolset. It helps security teams, QA and developers test SIP-based VoIP systems and applications. This toolset is useful in simulating VoIP hacking attacks against PBX systems especially through identification, scanning, extension enumeration and password cracking.",
